description.narrative: By 2021, Country Offices will have strengthened technical capacity to implement multi-sectoral scalable and evidence-based programmes aimed at preventing and responding to child marriage and FGM,which contributes to Harmful Practices (Fgm/C And Child Marriage). UNICEF aims to achieve this through Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: Every Child is protected from Violence, Exploitation and Harmful Practices.
